{"tid":1602794,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"全香港醫護同我入撚晒黎","createTime":"2019-09-29T13:52:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T12:50:06.000Z","uid":206176,"like":15,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"0196e6567215b657edba62efe7849aeb66c1e2e6","tid":1602794,"uid":206176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T13:52:41.000Z","msg":"立即停止救助黑警<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我都知你地有職業操守<br />\n一開波就讀日內瓦條約<br />\n但問題係<br />\n警察都有警察通例<br />\n都有學堂宣誓<br />\n但佢地而家公然違法<br />\n有法不依<br />\n佢地break左社會契約<br />\n你仲死版咁守約做乜9<br />\n你繼續救黑警<br />\n只係教條式思想<br />\n到咁關鍵時刻<br />\n請大家幫忙加強施壓<br />\n同埋你諗下你救完佢<br />\n佢又出去打9d無辜婦孺<br />\n再要你地執手尾<br />\n你救完佢地<br />\n再出去強姦非禮整浮屍<br />\n咁撚on9嘅野都做？？<br />\n佢地仲要話唔撚洗你地救啊<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wH4HSE3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwH4HSE3.jpg&h=8b5235d7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ECZ45Z3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FECZ45Z3.jpg&h=bcf88cd8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/S4jHSE4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FS4jHSE4.jpg&h=a05b8760&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/62V4myp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F62V4myp.jpg&h=fe334f12&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e4da3d1a1039043fc912b8d44207ffd0c80350aa","tid":1602794,"uid":104811,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T13:53:08.000Z","msg":"聽日 930 全港三罷"},{"pid":"7092bb471ad1ed4d3e029fd8985d1ca5f983917e","tid":1602794,"uid":258758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T13:53:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c500aaa28bdc3ae00eb60d1519018ab0016b536","tid":1602794,"uid":206176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T13:53:30.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"3e8dfc15281b9502e3a478de0955af4a3f3478ce","tid":160